List of possible voice recognition API's we will consider using when we integrate this into our project

https://www.raywenderlich.com/60870/building-ios-app-like-siri
^^ability to record and playback, returns list of text results, uses server, made to be used with swift projects, includes detailed tutorial

https://github.com/api-ai/api-ai-cocoa-swift
^^very simple, easy integrated into swift project via cocoa pods

https://tryolabs.com/blog/2015/06/15/tlsphinx-automatic-speech-recognition-asr-in-swift/

http://www.politepix.com/openears/
^ no cost and complete offline (more privacy)

